-**Produces**: `docs/plans/<ordinal>-<slug>/<slug>-plan.md` with the Gate Matrix (G1–G7) + Status header — plus inline `⚠️ GAP:` markers and a final `## Unresolved Gaps` table on any gate FAIL. Terminal report: plan path · Status · phase/task/domain counts · gate tally.
